node.text:
Ad COMPETITION - If you are looking for a little gift inspo then take a look @oliviaburtonlondon 💕They sponsored me to gift a loved one a gift and I found the most stunning watch and bracelet for my bestie (take a peek at my story to see it). They are such a classic yet feminine pieces (she’s obsessed with rose gold too)! So now you can give a little love....❤️ Olivia Burton is giving you the chance to win a gift for your loved one.
To enter, head to @oliviaburtonlondon and comment on the competition post tagging your nominee. Besure to tell them which Olivia Burton piece was made just for them and why!
T&Cs apply
#GiftOliviaBurton
